    "Moreover, there exists a constant C > 0 such that b hk ij (cos θ) ≤ C| cos θ|| sin θ| ∀θ ∈ [0, π].",
    "The first hypothesis (CH1) translates part of the micro-reversibility property for reactions and is very natural.",
